html: He—The Lord. Shook—Heb. he made the kingdoms to tremble; the neighbouring and confederate kingdoms, who might justly quake at her fall, for the dreadfulness and unexpectedness of the thing; and because Tyre was a bulwark, and a refuge to them. A commandment—Hath put this design into the hearts of her enemies, and given them courage to attempt, and strength to execute it.
